      "en": "Volume 49 Book of Later Tang 25: Biographies 1 - Empresses and Consorts",
      "raw": "卷四十九 唐書25: 后妃列傳一 Volume 49 Book of Later Tang 25: Biographies 1 - Empresses and Consorts"
